SyntheticaDockingViewTitlebarUI
public class BasicDockingViewTitlebarUI
extends DockingViewTitlebarUI

Basic UI implementation for titleBar.

Optional UI-Properties:

  • JYDocking.titlebar.font.name - String, default is regular panel font name.
  • JYDocking.titlebar.font.style - String, default is "PLAIN", supported values "PLAIN", "BOLD", "ITALIC".
  • JYDocking.titlebar.font.size - Integer, default is regular panel font size.
  • JYDocking.titlebar.foreground - Color, default is Color.BLACK.
  • JYDocking.titlebar.active.foreground - Color, default is Color.BLACK.
  • JYDocking.titlebar.insets - Insets, default is 3,4,1,4.
  • JYDocking.dockingButtonFactory.className - String, default "de.javasoft.swing.plaf.jydocking.DockingButtonFactory".
